\[\bar{Y}-\bar{X}-t_{m+n-2,\,1-CL}\,S_{p}\sqrt{\frac{1}{m}+\frac{1}{n}}\qquad \text{and}\qquad\bar{Y}-\bar{X}+t_{m+n-2,\,1-CL}\,S_{p}\sqrt{\frac{1}{m}+\frac{ 1}{n}},\]

